parameter_description: Turns the arpeggiator on or off
Sets what comes out of MIDI channel A's CV output
usage: 0: note; 1: velocity; 2: modulation; 3-127: LFO (rate set by clock out)

parameter_description: Sets what comes out of MIDI channel B's CV output
usage: 0: note; 1: velocity; 2: modulation; 3-127: LFO (rate set to <TAP> PGM_A)

parameter_description: Sets what comes out of MIDI channel A's gate output
usage: 0: note on; 1: velocity > 50%; 2: mod wheel > 50%; 3-127: LFO

parameter_description: Sets what comes out of MIDI channel B's gate output
usage: 0: note on; 1: velocity > 50%; 2: mod wheel > 50%; 3-127: LFO

parameter_description: Sets the amount of bend on MIDI channel A, in semitones
Sets the amount of bend on MIDI channel B, in semitones
Sets the amount of aftertouch on MIDI channel A, in semitones
Sets the amount of aftertouch on MIDI channel B, in semitones
Sets the minimum velocity value for MIDI channel A
Sets the minimum velocity value for MIDI channel B
Turns the MIDI clock on or off
Divides the tempo in as reflected in clock out
